{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"With all the legitimate concerns\nabout AIDS and avian flu --"},{"time":3000,"text":"and we'll hear about that from the"},{"time":5000,"text":"brilliant Dr. Brilliant later today --"},{"time":7000,"text":"I want to talk about the other\npandemic, which is"},{"time":9358,"text":"cardiovascular disease,\ndiabetes, hypertension --"},{"time":12000,"text":"all of which are completely\npreventable for at"},{"time":15000,"text":"least 95 percent of people"},{"time":17000,"text":"just by changing diet and lifestyle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18000,"text":"And what's happening is that there's a"},{"time":19000,"text":"globalization of illness\noccurring, that people"},{"time":21263,"text":"are starting to eat like us,\nand live like us, and"},{"time":24000,"text":"die like us. And\nin one generation, for example,"},{"time":27000,"text":"Asia's gone from having\none of the lowest rates of"},{"time":29000,"text":"heart disease and obesity\nand diabetes to one"},{"time":31167,"text":"of the highest. And in Africa,\ncardiovascular disease"},{"time":34000,"text":"equals the HIV and AIDS deaths"},{"time":37000,"text":"in most countries."},{"time":38000,"text":"So there's a critical\nwindow of opportunity we"},{"time":40000,"text":"have to make an important\ndifference that can"},{"time":42000,"text":"affect the lives of literally\nmillions of people,"},{"time":44000,"text":"and practice preventive\nmedicine on a global"},{"time":46120,"text":"scale."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47000,"text":"Heart and blood vessel\ndiseases still kill more"},{"time":49215,"text":"people -- not only in this\ncountry, but also"},{"time":51335,"text":"worldwide -- than everything\nelse combined, and yet"},{"time":54000,"text":"it's completely preventable\nfor almost everybody."},{"time":57000,"text":"It's not only preventable; it's actually"},{"time":59000,"text":"reversible. And for the last\nalmost 29 years,"},{"time":61167,"text":"we've been able to show\nthat by simply changing"},{"time":63430,"text":"diet and lifestyle, using\nthese very high-tech,"},{"time":66000,"text":"expensive, state-of-the-art\nmeasures to prove how"},{"time":68358,"text":"powerful these very simple\nand low-tech and low-cost"},{"time":71000,"text":"interventions can be like -- quantitative"},{"time":73000,"text":"arteriography,\nbefore and after a year, and"},{"time":75072,"text":"cardiac PET scans."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76000,"text":"We showed a few months\nago -- we published the"},{"time":78000,"text":"first study showing you\ncan actually stop or"},{"time":80120,"text":"reverse the progression\nof prostate cancer by"},{"time":82287,"text":"making changes in diet\nand lifestyle, and 70 percent"},{"time":85000,"text":"regression in the tumor\ngrowth, or inhibition of"},{"time":89000,"text":"the tumor growth, compared\nto only nine percent in the"},{"time":91000,"text":"control group."},{"time":92000,"text":"And in the MRI and MR\nspectroscopy here, the"},{"time":94120,"text":"prostate tumor activity\nis shown in red -- you can"},{"time":96120,"text":"see it diminishing after a year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98000,"text":"Now there is an epidemic\nof obesity: two-thirds of"},{"time":101000,"text":"adults and 15 percent of kids.\nWhat's really concerning"},{"time":104000,"text":"to me is that diabetes has\nincreased 70 percent in the"},{"time":107000,"text":"past 10 years, and this may be the first"},{"time":109000,"text":"generation in which our kids\nlive a shorter life"},{"time":111000,"text":"span than we do. That's pitiful, and it's"},{"time":113000,"text":"preventable."},{"time":114000,"text":"Now these are not election\nreturns, these are the"},{"time":117000,"text":"people -- the number\nof the people who are obese"},{"time":119310,"text":"by state, beginning in '85,\n'86, '87 -- these are"},{"time":123000,"text":"from the CDC website --\n'88, '89, '90, '91 -- you"},{"time":127000,"text":"get a new category --\n'92, '93, '94, '95, '96,"},{"time":131000,"text":"'97, '98, '99, 2000, 2001\n-- it gets worse. We're"},{"time":136000,"text":"kind of devolving. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":141000,"text":"Now what can we do about this?\nWell, you know, the"},{"time":144000,"text":"diet that we've found\nthat can reverse heart"},{"time":145000,"text":"disease and cancer is an Asian diet."},{"time":147000,"text":"But the people in Asia\nare starting to eat like we"},{"time":149000,"text":"are, which is why they're\nstarting to get sick"},{"time":150000,"text":"like we are."},{"time":151000,"text":"So I've been working\nwith a lot of the big food"},{"time":153000,"text":"companies. They can make\nit fun and sexy and hip"},{"time":155000,"text":"and crunchy and convenient\nto eat healthier foods,"},{"time":157405,"text":"like -- I chair the advisory\nboards to McDonald's,"},{"time":160000,"text":"and PepsiCo, and ConAgra,\nand Safeway, and soon"},{"time":162000,"text":"Del Monte, and they're\nfinding that it's good"},{"time":164167,"text":"business."},{"time":165000,"text":"The salads that you see\nat McDonald's came from"},{"time":166000,"text":"the work -- they're going\nto have an Asian salad. At"},{"time":168000,"text":"Pepsi, two-thirds\nof their revenue growth came"},{"time":170000,"text":"from their better foods."}]},{"cues":[{"time":171000,"text":"And so if we can do that,\nthen we can free up"},{"time":173167,"text":"resources for buying drugs\nthat you really do need"},{"time":176000,"text":"for treating AIDS and HIV\nand malaria and for"},{"time":179000,"text":"preventing avian flu. Thank you."}]}]}